reviewText: Talk about an old goodie. Really enjoyed this railroad film. To non railroad people it is likely lost that the Santa Fe 3000 series locomotives only ran for a couple years being the largest locos in the world at the time. This this is a very rare coverage. It is a must for railfans.
IF YOU LIKE CLIFFHANGERS AND SILENT MOVIES, THESE ARE VERY INTERESTING.  THEY ARE WELL DONE.  IF I REMEMBER COREECTLY, HOWEVER, THE SOUNDTRACK WAS NOT TOO GOOD.
